metadata.name: 19x19 Midgame Positions (Multiprocess Enhanced KataGo, Moves 100,150,200) (Equal Prisoners) (Both Colors)
metadata.description: Midgame positions from Go games on 19x19 boards at move numbers 100,150,200, with KataGo analysis, equal prisoner checking, both color evaluation, ownership discretization (step=0.125), move sequence tracking, generated using multiprocessing with 2 workers
